com.ibm.zrl.idmx.key
Class IssuerPrivateKey

java.lang.Object
  com.ibm.zrl.idmx.key.IssuerPrivateKey

public class IssuerPrivateKey
extends java.lang.Object

The Issuer private key (signing key) for the CL signature scheme. Required to issue certificates. In addition to the key itself, this object contains the corresponding system parameters.

See Also:
IssuerPublicKey, IssuerKeyPair
